column2: SELECT s.specobjid, s.z, g.lgm_tot_p5#, m.logMass FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN SpecObjAll s ON s.specObjID = x.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra g ON g.specObjID = x.specObjID  JOIN stellarMassPassivePort m ON m.specObjID = x.specObjID ORDER by x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
